# =============================================================================
# DEVELOPMENT NOTES
# =============================================================================
#
# API Connection:
# - Development: JavaScript detects localhost and uses http://localhost:8080/api
# - Production: JavaScript uses /api (relative URL, Ingress routes to backend)
#
# See: src/utils/api.ts for the implementation
#
# To start development:
#   cd frontend
#   npm install
#   npm run dev
#
# Or use docker-compose from project root:
#   ./scripts/dev.sh
#
